node.text:
🚨Want a Surprise FREE™ Pizza Party on us?! 🚨 Thru 11/21/21, to enter for your chance to WIN:​⁣
⁣
1. Post a picture of the Surprise Free you got with your online delivery order on Instagram or Twitter​⁣
2. Use the hashtags #FreesNotFees & #Sweepstakes​⁣
⁣
NO PURCHASE NECESSARY.  Legal residents of the 50 U.S. (D.C.), 13 +. Enter by 11/21/21 at 11:59 p.m. ET.  For Official Rules, including how to enter by mail, odds, & prize details, see rules in bio. Void where prohibited.
